Package com.ibm.di.config.base

Class InternalSchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.di.config.base.InternalSchema
  • public class InternalSchema
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines all the parameter names used in other Configuration classes as String constants, to make it easier to use the same name everywhere.
